    <item>
      <title>加密货币繁荣之际，芝加哥期权交易所 (Cboe) 将推出以现金结算的比特币 ETF 期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/cboe-to-launch-cash-settled-bitcoin-etf-options-as-crypto-booms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cboe Global Markets Inc. 表示，即将推出首个与比特币现货价格相关的现金结算指数期权，这是传统交易所新增加密货币相关证券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/cboe-to-launch-cash-settled-bitcoin-etf-options-as-crypto-booms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 16:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毕达哥拉斯加密基金回报率达 230%，超过比特币的涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/pythagoras-crypto-fund-returns-230-to-outpace-bitcoin-s-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年年底，Mitchell Dong 发现了一个机会：现货比特币 ETF 即将面向美国投资者推出，他希望自己的加密对冲基金能够提供表现更佳的竞争产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/pythagoras-crypto-fund-returns-230-to-outpace-bitcoin-s-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gensler 退出计划导致美国证券交易委员会瞄准的加密代币数量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/crypto-tokens-xrp-ada-sol-targeted-by-sec-jump-on-gensler-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国证券交易委员会主席、业界头号反对者加里·根斯勒 (Gary Gensler) 宣布计划辞职后，被美国证券交易委员会标记为未注册证券的数字资产正在上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/crypto-tokens-xrp-ada-sol-targeted-by-sec-jump-on-gensler-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 希望在特朗普时代上线更多 Memecoin</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-11-21/coinbase-hopes-to-list-more-memecoins-in-the-trump-era</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Suvashree Ghosh 与 Coinbase 高管讨论了唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫将如何导致更多 memecoin 在美国最大的加密货币交易所上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-11-21/coinbase-hopes-to-list-more-memecoins-in-the-trump-era</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 22:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一旦法规发生变化，Charles Schwab 将关注现货加密货币交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/charles-schwab-eyes-spot-crypto-trading-once-regulations-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉信理财公司即将上任的首席执行官里克·沃斯特 (Rick Wurster) 表示，一旦美国法规允许，该公司将考虑提供现货加密货币交易 - 一旦当选总统唐纳德·特朗普上任，这种情况就更有可能发生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/charles-schwab-eyes-spot-crypto-trading-once-regulations-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 20:48:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 扩大支付业务，计划进行更多收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/coinbase-eyes-more-acquisitions-as-it-expands-payments-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Coinbase Global Inc. 正在加大在数字支付领域的投入，希望进行更多收购并从该业务线中创造更多收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/coinbase-eyes-more-acquisitions-as-it-expands-payments-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 18:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Calamos Investments 希望通过新的 ETF 对冲比特币的波动性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/the-etf-world-s-100-hedging-crew-wants-to-break-into-bitcoin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[承诺对冲全球最大加密货币剧烈波动的交易所交易基金可能很快就会登陆华尔街，此前，该货币经历了三位数的上涨，将投机热情推向了一个全新的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/the-etf-world-s-100-hedging-crew-wants-to-break-into-bitcoin</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 17:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citron Research 做空 MicroStrategy 股票后股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/microstrategy-tumbles-after-citron-research-shorts-the-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前 Andrew Left 的 Citron Research 在 X 上的一篇文章中表示，其正在做空这家软件公司，随后 MicroStrategy Inc 的股价暴跌，该公司实际上已将自己转变为一个比特币投资基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/microstrategy-tumbles-after-citron-research-shorts-the-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:22:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币创纪录上涨，美国 ETF 资产飙升至 1000 亿美元以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/record-bitcoin-btc-run-sees-us-etf-assets-surge-to-over-100-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着比特币延续创纪录的涨势，直接投资于比特币的美国交易所交易基金总资产超过 1000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/record-bitcoin-btc-run-sees-us-etf-assets-surge-to-over-100-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 07:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
